Interface IntentI

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Intent

    public interface IntentI
extends java.io.Serializable
    The interface IntentI must be implemented by intent submitted to a ComputerCoordinator to notify that you want to change the state of the computer

    Description

    Intent can be on Computer's Cores number or frequency
    Author:
    jaunecitron
